; Coverage for times.cc lines 1169-1170: daily period duration

2024/01/01 Test1
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Cash

2024/01/02 Test2
    Expenses:Food    $20.00
    Assets:Cash

test reg Expenses --daily
24-Jan-01 - 24-Jan-01           Expenses:Food                $10.00       $10.00
24-Jan-02 - 24-Jan-02           Expenses:Food                $20.00       $30.00
end test
